        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Are you searching for the best jewelry for fashion that truly elevates your style and complements every outfit? Jewelry is no longer just an accessory—it’s a way to express personality, confidence, and taste. The best jewelry for fashion in 2025 combines timeless elegance with modern trends, ensuring that each piece works for everyday wear, office settings, parties, and special milestones.</p><p>In this guide, we will explore the top jewelry pieces that are trending and timeless, provide detailed styling tips for every occasion, and explain how to choose pieces that are both sustainable and luxurious. By the end, you will know how to curate a collection of the best jewelry for fashion that reflects your personal style, stands out in any setting, and highlights ethical and conscious choices with brands like Lucira Jewelry.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Jewelry Is the Heart of Fashion?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Jewelry Is the Heart of Fashion?</h2>",
            "custom_id": "heart",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_gEUkmH": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Model_976e73cd-52d8-41f7-bf68-3ff440ca907f.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Jewelry is the soul of fashion. The best jewelry for fashion transforms simple outfits into iconic looks and adds personality to even the most basic wardrobe. Accessories such as rings, bracelets, earrings, and necklaces allow individuals to make statements without saying a word.</p><p>Fashion-forward individuals understand that the right jewelry enhances confidence and style. The best jewelry for fashion in 2025 focuses not only on aesthetic appeal but also on versatility and sustainability. From lab-grown diamond solitaires to layered chains, jewelry pieces can move seamlessly between casual settings, office wear, and glamorous evening events.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "3-60cts-brilliant-round-six-prong-solitaire-stud-earrings",
